  <Features
    id="features"
    title="What do you write about?"
    subtitle="We write about anything and everything that involves the suffering of humans in and all shapes and sizes. "
    columns={2}
    items={[
      {
        title: 'Handpicked topics',
        description:
          'We carefully research and sometimes even put ourselves on location to get information about the stories we are concerned with',
        icon: 'tabler:bulb',
      },
      {
        title: 'Thorough dives',
        description: `We cover the good and the bad, no matter who it affects in the long run. We have no tribe except the tribe of humanity.`,
        icon: 'tabler:layers-intersect',
      },
      {
        title: 'From Palestine to the Congo',
        description:
          'We dont only focus on the trendy stories of suffering. Were here to connect the dots about how suffering is connected to all aspects of our lives whether its cobalt mining in the Congo, to oil wells off the coast of Gaza.',
        icon: 'tabler:palette',
      },
      {
        title: 'Our DMs are open',
        description: `Do you have an interesting topic you want us to cover or research? Shoot us a DM and we'll look into it. `,
        icon: 'tabler:podium',
      },
    ]}
  />

